                    <h3>Divorce (Talaq)</h3>
                    <p>Clear, confidential guidance through divorce and talaq for DHA clients, protecting your rights every step of the way.</p>
                    <div class="service-footer">
                        <a href="/services/divorce-custody-case/" class="service-link">Learn More <span class="service-arrow">&#8594;</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon-wrapper">
                        <span class="service-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="21"/><path d="M5 7h14"/><path d="M5 7l-3 6a3 3 0 0 0 6 0z"/><path d="M19 7l-3 6a3 3 0 0 0 6 0z"/><path d="M8 21h8"/></svg></span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Khula</h3>
